    "updated_at": "2015-08-04T00:16:02Z",
    "body": "Conceptually though this seems like the obvious construction - making separate BufReaders for each take call seems extremely backwards. Also take(0) behaving differently on BufReader from Read (even if only on BufRead methods) seems weird.\n",
